description:
This is a 10 minute workout called 'Beginners Indoor Cycle Workout | Home Workout | Ideal World' from the channel Ideal World.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.

Original workout description: Join Tim Britton, fitness trainer, personal instructor and Ideal World's fitness coach as he guides you through a beginners workout with an indoor cycle or exercise bike. If you find this workout a little too easy, simply increase the resistance on your indoor bike and repeat the workout!
